Hey, watch the suit. Watch the suit.

25:41.959 --> 25:44.667
Compelling drama, gentlemen,
but we do need to get him into bed.

25:44.751 --> 25:46.167
- You take the head.
- Why?

25:46.251 --> 25:48.626
