- Who are you, Nijinsky? Come on.
- I have a bad back.

26:04.376 --> 26:06.126
Too much social climbing, I expect.

26:06.251 --> 26:08.917
- The head is the heaviest part.
- All right, ready?

26:09.251 --> 26:11.084
