26:32.376 --> 26:34.626
Go. Right, go.

26:34.792 --> 26:36.272
- Get back to the kitchen now!
- Move!

26:36.417 --> 26:37.626
- Move!
- Now. Now.

26:38.417 --> 26:40.292
