26:40.376 --> 26:43.376
- Do you think Stalin's too heavy?
- No, it's a compliment.

26:43.459 --> 26:44.959
- Gold is heavy.
- Well, you'd know.

26:45.084 --> 26:47.167
You've looted enough of it,
you saucy little pirate.

26:47.292 --> 26:49.167
Get back in the dining room!

26:49.751 --> 26:52.376
- Right, this one. This way, this way.
- Stop using his feet.

26:52.501 --> 26:54.167
- I'm sorry.
- Can we just put him down?

26:54.292 --> 26:56.626
- I'm absolutely soaked.
- Lamp. Lamp, lamp.

26:56.751 --> 26:59.084
- Out of the way.
- No, wait a minute... move, move.

26:59.209 --> 27:01.209
Mikoyan,
