29:48.459 --> 29:51.542
Comrade Timashuk,
I retired six years ago.

29:51.626 --> 29:53.334
- Get that coat on him.
- Please, I...

29:53.792 --> 29:55.376
Look,
I can give you names.

29:55.459 --> 29:58.167
- Come on. Stop resisting.
- What about my dog?

29:58.251 --> 29:59.876
- This is appalling.
- Hurry up.

30:01.459 --> 30:02.584
Get him in the van.

30:03.376 --> 30:04.959
We found some old friends of yours.

30:05.626 --> 30:07.584
I've never met them
before in my life.

30:14.126 --> 30:16.084
So, Molotov's off the list.

30:16.167 --> 30:18.667
Yes, Beria's moving fast.

30:19.542 --> 30:21.126
But we can still outvote him.

30:21.292 --> 30:26.042
I always thought it would be you,
to fill Stalin's shoes, if I'm honest.

30:26.126 --> 30:27.459
Not Malenkov.

30:30.917 --> 30:32.834
Who knows the future
of the Union?

30:33.834 --> 30:36.667
Well, the Union
could really use change.

30:37.501 --> 30:39.501
Maybe some reforms
now that the old man...

30:39.626 --> 30:41.251
No, Nicky.

30:41.876 --> 30:44.042
Nobody needs factionalism.

30:45.042 --> 30:46.542
You want factionalism?

30:46.751 --> 30:49.501
What about those two, fucking
Abbott and Costello over there?

30:49.626 --> 30:51.126
Christ.

30:51.251 --> 30:54.501
When I piss, I try to make
eye contact with an officer.

30:54.626 --> 30:55.876
Ruins their day.

30:56.667 --> 30:59.751
When I piss, I try to piss
on an officer. Also ruins their day.

31:00.876 --> 31:02.751
We should keep an eye
on Kaganovich.

31:02.959 --> 31:05.251
Yeah, Khrushchev too,
his talking goat.

31:05.334 --> 31:08.709
Khrushchev. I spend my life
making people talk.

31:08.792 --> 31:11.292
I can't shut that gabbling idiot up.

31:12.584 --> 31:15.542
We need to assert our authority,
increase security in Moscow.

31:15.709 --> 31:17.542
We should get
Stalin's children here.

31:17.667 --> 31:20.876
Vasily will be lying face down
in a ditch full of vodka.

31:21.001 --> 31:23.584
- But Svetlana...
- The people love her.

31:23.667 --> 31:25.876
- I'm gonna get her in.
- Comrade ministers!

31:26.001 --> 31:30.001
- Svetlana is here!
- I'm here. I'm over here!

31:30.084 --> 31:32.209
- Svetlana!
- Svetlana!

31:32.292 --> 31:33.959
Shit. The race has started.

31:34.084 --> 31:37.626
All right, we need to start putting
together a plan. We need change.

31:37.751 --> 31:39.876
Put a halt to the arrests,
prison releases,

31:40.001 --> 31:41.417
maybe even reform the Church.

31:41.542 --> 31:43.542
How can you run and plot
at the same time?

31:43.667 --> 31:44.834
Hello! Svetlana!

31:44.959 --> 31:46.584
- They're trying to cut you off.
- Where?

31:46.667 --> 31:48.334
It's obvious. Svetlana!

31:48.417 --> 31:49.876
- Svetlana!
- Svetlana!

31:49.959 --> 31:52.001
- Oh, my darling.
- Where is he?

31:52.084 --> 31:54.251
- Where's my father? I would like...
- Oh, my dear.

31:54.334 --> 31:57.167
- I'm so sorry.
- I would like to see him.

31:57.251 --> 31:59.292
- Yes, of course.
- Where is he?

31:59.376 --> 32:01.334
We'll take you inside. He's in bed.

32:01.626 --> 32:03.792
God Almighty!
Look at that herb garden.

32:03.876 --> 32:05.018
Does nobody tend it any more?

32:05.042 --> 32:07.459
Do people no longer
eat herbs any more?

32:07.542 --> 32:08.959
Do they only eat weeds?

32:09.084 --> 32:11.268
- Come on, we'll take you to see him.
- Where is Vasily?

32:11.292 --> 32:13.167
- I will get your brother here.
- Most helpful.

32:13.292 --> 32:15.126
- All right.
- She wants Vasily.

32:15.251 --> 32:18.792
