33:14.376 --> 33:17.209
- Or I'll have you killed, okay?
- Apologies. And agreed.

33:17.334 --> 33:19.126
Or I'll just do it myself.

33:20.167 --> 33:22.334
Come on! Play on!

33:23.209 --> 33:25.126
Play through! Ignore me!

33:25.209 --> 33:28.626
