Do they know about the crash?

33:35.917 --> 33:38.459
Give me a drink. I've got time
for a drink. Give me the flask.

33:38.542 --> 33:39.584
No, no.

33:42.251 --> 33:43.792
You are to come
to your father's dacha.

33:43.876 --> 33:45.268
The plane should never have taken off.

33:45.292 --> 33:47.292
