happened to our national team?

33:51.876 --> 33:53.917
- Nothing's happened.
- What the fuck are you doing?

33:54.084 --> 33:56.417
My father will have you saddled
and ridden to Siberia,

33:56.542 --> 33:58.084
you rude fucking pies.

33:59.459 --> 34:02.292
These are good doctors,
my dear. They're the best.

34:02.417 --> 34:04.209
