35:56.001 --> 36:00.251
- Moscow's closed. No-one gets in.
- Especially you.

36:00.334 --> 36:03.042
NKVD to displace army officers
at every station.

36:07.417 --> 36:09.792
Army back to barracks.
We're taking over.

36:10.334 --> 36:12.459
Remove Molotov from that last list.

36:15.334 --> 36:16.501
