01:25:47.876 --> 01:25:49.417
Saddle up, cowboy.

01:25:49.501 --> 01:25:53.292
- Is Malenkov with us?
- Trust me, 100 percent.

01:25:53.376 --> 01:25:54.584
Yes!

01:25:54.792 --> 01:25:57.542
- So you're on board, then, Molotov?
- Yeah.

